description:
Vocals: Changed the instrument of the lead vocals, made a few minor rhythm fixes, made some notes more connected, and added lyrics for both vocal tracks.

Lead Guitar: Changed the instrument from overdrive guitar to distortion guitar. Also changed the riff to how Dave actually plays it, and removed the parts where it was playing what the rhythm guitar was playing.

Rhythm guitars: Corrected the slide down at the beginning so it wasn't just one note without a slide, fixed the chords so they played the proper ones in the intro, and fixed some slides throughout the song.
title: Monkey Wrench
